│ the original samesign icmp.                                                 │
│                                                                             │
│ This indicates a bug in `foldBooleanAndOr` - it should be returning a       │
│ regular icmp but isn't.                                                     │
│                                                                             │
│ Given this, the correct fix is to ensure that when we have a samesign icmp  │
│ in this context, we either:                                                 │
│ 1. Don't transform at all, or                                               │
│ 2. Transform to an AND operation which is always safe                       │
│                                                                             │
│ Since the AND operation `CondVal & TrueVal` is always poison-safe (because  │
│ `and false, poison = false`), the safest approach is to create the AND      │
│ operation explicitly.                                                       │
